articles.title: Ireland's president-elect is a left-wing, anti-establishment figure who is outspoken on Gaza - NPR
articles.description: Ireland's president for the next seven years is an independent lawmaker who has long spoken in support of Palestinians and has been vocal about her distrust of European Union policies.
